Definition: usually plural) an expression of pleasure at the success or good fortune of another
Example: I sent them my sincere congratulations on their marriage
Synonyms: verb, emotion, congratulate, communication, felicitation, felicitate, expression, noun, plural, u, usually, an, of, pleasure, at, the, success, or, good, fortune, another, I, sent, them, my, sincere, congratulations, on, their, marriage
Category: noun.communication
